title: Ep 14: Milk Sucks
description:
Today's Proceedings:  We take a look at toxic masculinity by talking about women being good at video games and how selling nudes is not empowering to women! We also discuss what it's like to be a woman on the internet and the adventures of HottGirl99.  Lastly, we discuss r/Love and what true love really looks like.

Rate and Review our podcast and share it with your friends!
